title: Perfect Roasted Chicken With Croutons and Fish-Sauce Butter | Eric Kim | NYT Cooking
description:
Eric's new recipe has it all: crispy-skinned chicken thighs, schmaltzy croutons and a flavorful, buttery pan sauce. (And, because it's Eric, he went for extra credit with the most beautiful loaf of homemade bread.)

Get the recipe: https://nyti.ms/3wWnc6I
